dataset.title: Runways of Sky Harbor International Airport, Phoenix Arizona - year 1999

abstract.para: This layer contains the runways of Sky Harbor International Airport, Phoenix Arizona in 1999. This dataset was produced by the Central Arizona-Phoenix long term ecological research project.
